# Choosing compute — the cheat sheet

- **Interactive dev** / notebook exploration → all-purpose cluster
- **Scheduled production ETL** → job cluster (ephemeral, cheaper, isolated)
- **BI dashboards & ad-hoc SQL** → SQL warehouse (serverless for best start + price)
- **Bursty / don't-manage-infra** → serverless compute (seconds to start, no idle cost)
- **ML training** → all-purpose or job cluster on the ML runtime
